    "paragraph_or_text_span": "At the preoperative outpatient appointment, review and expand on the topics in recommendation 1.1.2, and give people information about: the refractive implications of different intraocular lenses (see recommendation 1.5.3) types of anaesthesia the person's individual risk of complications during or after surgery (for example, the risk of postoperative retinal detachment in people with high myopia;",
